trans-unit.source: The [/target](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/target-compiler-option.md) compiler option was used, but an invalid parameter was passed.

trans-unit.source: To resolve this error, recompile the program using the form of the **/target** option that is appropriate to your output file.
